Below is a turnkey-ready content kit you can hand straight to design & engineering.  
It keeps every fact, metric, and technique you already approved, but tightens the story arc, clarifies the voice, and adds a full image brief (style, ratio, usage, alt-text) for every asset—so your devs, designers and procurement teams know exactly what to create or license.

---

