STORY.HTML  (Scrollytelling)
================================================================
Concept  
Five fixed “chapters” pinned with GSAP ScrollTrigger; background swaps, headline + kicker animate in; body copy slides left→right.

Tone tweaks  
• Change “A laptop, $300 in cloud credits, and Sylhet underwater.” →  
  “One laptop, $300 in cloud credits—Sylhet was already under water.”  
• End each chapter with a metric tag pill for rhythm.

Layout skeleton  
```
<section id="chapter-1" class="pinned">
   <img class="bg" src="/assets/img/story/01-flood-sar.jpg" … />
   <div class="copy">
        <h2>The Constraint</h2>
        <p>…</p>
        <span class="tag">91 % mIoU</span>
   </div>
</section>
… (repeat)
```

