================================================================
ACCESSIBILITY & PERFORMANCE CHECKLIST
================================================================
1. Alt-text provided for 100 % of images.  
2. All videos <8 MB H.264, provide `.webm` fallback + lazy-load.  
3. Use `prefers-reduced-motion` media query to freeze parallax for motion-sensitive users.  
4. Color contrast ≥4.5:1 for text vs background.  
5. Largest Contentful Paint (LCP) target <2.5 s: hero images pre-rendered in `srcset` with `sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1920px"`.

================================================================
VOICE & STYLE GUARDRAILS
================================================================
• Sentence length: average 13–17 words.  
• 1 technical noun = 1 metric. Ex: “SegFormer-B2 (24 M params).”  
• Zero adjectives without evidence; keep the “number + noun” pattern (e.g., “95 % extraction accuracy” instead of “high accuracy”).  
• Occasional poetic hook every ~150 words to humanise (already injected).

